# 32-byte secp256k1 secret. Accepts:
#   - 0x-prefixed 64-char hex (industry standard, MetaMask export, viem)
#   - bare 64-char hex
#   - InFlow's Java seed: Hex.encodeHexString(BigInteger.toByteArray())
#     (66 hex chars with leading "00" for ~half of keys; short hex
#     allowed when BigInteger stripped leading zero bytes).
EVM_PRIVATE_KEY=
TARGET_URL=http://localhost:3000/api/widgets
